@Node Main "UniversalGIO modules for Photogenics - Overview"
UniversalGIOModules 5.1 (c) by Helmut Hoffmann 1995-99
===================
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| The fast and flexible loader/saver modules for Photogenics (Almathera)        |
|  (this module is probably NOT usable with Photogenics demo or lite versions or|
|   forthcoming Photogenics NG programs which are not made by Almathera!)       |
| * fast loading of more than 20 file formats (incl. e.g. PhotoCD)              |
| * support for Datatype loading (now incl. support of 24Bit Datatypes)         |
| * downscaled loading support (load big pictures with few memory)              |
| * TrueColor animation creation saver for CyberGraphX (incl. Piccasso 96 soft) |
|   or EGS users                                                                |
| * automatic animation creation and conversion with included ARexx scripts     |
|   (Photogenics V2.0 or higher needed)                                         |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
